beastiary:int_siren_musker_clements a beast:Interpretation ;
    rdfs:comment "In the movie 'The Little SIren' the authors reverse the brutality of the original Anderson's tale, rewriting the images of terror into a positive happy ending. Through this euphemization of danger, the main character's voicr is not mutilated but safely kept in a shell. This inversion allows her to reach her dream of becoming a human and marrying the prince she fell in love with."@en ;
