beastiary:int_elf_moore a beast:Interpretation ;
    rdfs:comment "In Moore the elf is shrunk down to a tiny, non-threatening size following a cyclic symbol since it appears strictly at midnight on the winter solstice, directly tied to the calendar, the cold season, and the promise of festive renewal."@en ;
