    beast:ofCreature beastiary:creature_elf .

beastiary:int_elf_tolkien a beast:Interpretation ;
    rdfs:comment "In Sturluson the division of elves, the light-elves are ultimate spectacular symbols of solar clarity, floating high up in the branches of the world tree. In Tolkien they do not decay or wrinkle with time. They escape the 'gravitational pull' of human mortality."@en ;
