beastiary:int_siren_ovidius a beast:Interpretation ;
    rdfs:comment "Ovidio tells the story of sirens as creatures whose were gifted wings from the Gods to be able to search Persefone, kidnapped by Ade. In this interpretation they symbolize the conquering of a new power."@en ;
