beastiary:int_sphinx_apollodoro a beast:Interpretation ;
    rdfs:comment "The Theban sphinx fuses the diaretic riddle - the intellectual cut that separates truth from death - with the teriomorphic terror of the devouring monster who consumes those who fail to answer"@en ;
